                        "content": "A client who has a cold is seen in the emergency department with an inability to void. Because the client has a history of benign prostatic hyperplasia, the nurse determines that the client would be questioned about the use of which medication?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nIn the client with benign prostatic hyperplasia, episodes of urinary retention can be triggered by certain medications, such as decongestants, anticholinergics, and antidepressants. These medications lessen the voluntary ability to contract the bladder. The client needs to be questioned about the use of these medications if the client has urinary retention. Diuretics increase urine output. Antibiotics and antilipemics do not affect ability to urinate.",
                        "id": "2fe7f3ea966b46f6a44596b7112e7d09",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "b350df50789644408925c2e45ac98529",
                                "content": "Clear the nasal passages after use."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "be166b2bdcd847fdb960cb4bb097a9ca",
                                "content": "Take the medication only as needed."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "5d4d90c72666446e904063a08aaf3289",
                                "content": "The medication would start to work immediately."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "48a2417979a04ea8962be127833c9d24",
                                "content": "The medication works locally and decreases inflammation."
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
