                        "content": "A client is taking cetirizine. The nurse would inform the client of which side effect of this medication?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nCetirizine is an antihistamine; frequent side effects are drowsiness or sedation. Others include blurred vision, hypertension (and sometimes hypotension), dry mouth, constipation, urinary retention, and sweating. Therefore, the other options are incorrect.",
                        "id": "f82461d4762945548258e347b39a46b6",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
